    <string name="about_back">About Noor</string>
    <string name="about_hero_subtitle">Your daily spiritual companion toward the light</string>
    <string name="about_section_why_title">Why Noor?</string>
    <string name="about_section_why_body">Noor was created to help Muslims stay gently accountable to the deeds that matter most — Salah, Quran, Duas, and small acts of goodness — day after day. It is a quiet companion for consistency, not noise.</string>
    <string name="about_section_intention_title">This isn\'t a game</string>
    <string name="about_section_intention_body">Points and streaks are tools to build habits, not a measure of your worth before Allah. Noor is an accountability partner, not a scoreboard. Your sincerity is between you and your Lord — only He knows what is in your heart.</string>
    <string name="about_section_together_title">Grow together</string>
    <string name="about_section_together_body">Invite friends, cheer one another on, and let healthy competition draw you closer to good deeds. The leaderboard is meant to inspire, never to shame. We rise by lifting each other toward the light.</string>
